name: Aliens vs. Other aliens
description:
I can't test if the web version works or not.

An alien race has come to take over the earth. No, wait there's another one aaannnd now they're fighting over who gets to take over the planet below (earth).

Take control of an alien soldier blasting your way through the enemy mothership.

WASD - move
space - shoot

you can break cracked walls.
